headline: IDEXX Laboratories to Release 2025 Fourth Quarter and Full Year Financial Results
summary: WESTBROOK, Maine, January 09, 2026--IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (NASDAQ: IDXX), a global leader in pet healthcare innovation, has scheduled the release of its 2025 fourth quarter and full year financial results for Monday, February 2, 2026, before the market opens. The Company will conduct an analyst conference call beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET on that day.
